
Skycat/RTD/Catlib Source Distribution
-------------------------------------

This is the top level README file for the Skycat, RTD, and catalog
library packages. This directory contains a generic configure script
and Makefile that will build any of the packages in the correct order.
To simplify building the sources, the required utility packages
(astrotcl and tclutil) are also included here.

See the README files in the subdirectories for details on each
package.

The following URLs may also be of interest:

Skycat home page:
	http://archive.eso.org/skycat/

Postscript, PDF, and FrameMaker Documentation:
	ftp://ftp.archive.eso.org/pub/skycat/doc/

HTML Docs:
	http://arcdev.hq.eso.org/~archeso/skycat/skycat-man.html

Sources and binaries:
	ftp://ftp.archive.eso.org/pub/skycat/

